BEBOP SENSORS LAUNCHES 
		WEARABLE SMART FABRIC TECHNOLOGY --
		First Thin Smart Fabric Sensors to Measure All Aspects of Physicality: 
		
		Force, Location, Size, Twist, Bend, Stretch & Motion

Patented 
