BeBop is 
		now offering custom turnkey sensor solutions for OEMs to incorporate 
		into their products, ranging from basic sensors to complete wireless 
		solutions with advanced power management.  Visualization programs for 
		any design with an easily-modified SDK (Software Developer�s Kit) allows 
